question: Do you hate tyrus?
answer: Nah. I’m just not “about to have a stroke over them level” stan that 90% of the tag is. I just want to see a little more of TJ acting like a decent human being to Buffy first before Tyrus happens. And I want to see Tyrus develop on screen, none of that “surprise we’ve secretly been dating so now we can avoid showing development of a lgbt relationship on screen” bs.
